This prompt asks Claude to design the **Turnstyle Preflight Terms & Conditions Review Engine**.

Turnstyle generates **trade promotion Terms & Conditions** (primarily for Australian promotions).  
The Preflight Engine should automatically review generated terms before publication.

The goal is **compliance-oriented drafting review**, not legal advice.

The system should produce:

- Score out of 100
- Risk rating
- Critical issues
- Warnings
- Missing clauses
- Internal inconsistencies
- Builder-to-terms mismatches
- Suggested fixes
- Suggested rewrite wording
