# Issue Types

Please distinguish between:

### Critical Issues
Terms are not publication-ready.

### Warnings
Should be fixed before launch.

### Enhancements
Optional improvements.

### Missing Clauses
Expected clause absent.

### Internal Inconsistencies
Clauses conflict.

### Builder Mismatches
Builder data conflicts with text.

